{"tid":1014933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 成立研發團隊 擬生產自家 5G Modem 晶片","createTime":"2019-02-09T14:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T15:58:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf3e75f7ea233a706490459a735c4a6cae092f8","tid":1014933,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:51:38.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒日前報導指 Apple 有意設計自家的 Modem 晶片，未來將減少依賴其他生產商的供應。以往 Apple 依賴 Qualcomm 提供 Modem 晶片，但兩間公司最近涉及法律糾紛，Qualcomm 拒絕銷售晶片予 Apple，甚至在全球多國興訟要求 iPhone 停售。<br />\n<br />\n來源：gsmarena<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，Apple 向 Intel 採購的 Modem 晶片，效能卻比 Qualcomm 遜色，經過開發多款自家晶片後，消息指 Apple 決定自行開發 Modem 晶片。Apple 早前被發現在 Qualcomm 總部所在的聖地牙哥招聘，而公司亦組成 Modem 開發團隊，由硬件科技副總裁 Johny Srouji 領導。Srouji 在 2008 年開始在 Apple 工作，是首席晶片設計師，有份參予 A 系處理器和無線耳機 AirPods 的晶片設計工作。<br />\n<br />\n別期望在今年，甚至是明年的 iPhone 會見到 Apple 的自家 Modem 晶片，因為開發過程經年，而且花費不菲。加上今次 Apple 要開發的 Modem 晶片，不但要支持 4G 網絡，還要為 5G 網絡作準備。不過今次的投資長遠而言可能會為 Apple 節省成本，因為採用 Qualcomm 的 Modem，晶片本身就要 30 美元，而且對方還額外要求 7.5 美元授權費用。處理器和 Modem 都是自家開發，在整合度有望提高，以達到更佳的能源效益。<br />\n<br />\n來源：gsmarena<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=5cb6084f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=cab81d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=b92b24a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/09/apple-is-working-on-its-own-modem/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F09%2Fapple-is-working-on-its-own-modem%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=6BLFUKkZTytPAocRz50jI6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=327e0644\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/09/apple-is-working-on-its-own-modem/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"ba3e7c5cbf10e947056ab28f7bafcbd5d9e6abc8","tid":1014933,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔買左高通佢"},{"pid":"38e6939f175fa8c28a553e648294d4e17368d065","tid":1014933,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8a37b2446a24d43192fb6e87050bdaa22930ae2","tid":1014933,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38e6939f175fa8c28a553e648294d4e17368d065","tid":1014933,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba3e7c5cbf10e947056ab28f7bafcbd5d9e6abc8","tid":1014933,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔買左高通佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:05:33.000Z","msg":"買高通肯定要過哂全世界既反壟斷法規定<br />\n唔易過，又有排搞"},{"pid":"a8e3e87a1291acbea8da4ba089daf0102d38bd14","tid":1014933,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"Full of bug不是夢"},{"pid":"a111c7e08d0ff051054a1819baabbebd99df7017","tid":1014933,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:09:39.000Z","msg":"期望見到有一日apple起ai工廠自動組裝富士康同支那齊齊收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9635bc959fbdb59ffc102d3e4cea36d9c7b43737","tid":1014933,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"今次撐apple"},{"pid":"7b8bec7d0b0718031643cc4f64ba4368ef513396","tid":1014933,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"apple識開發晶片<img src=\"/assets/face